<h1>Adding custom mountpoints</h1>

<p>
  Simply update the configurations with the name, description and a path.
</p>

<p><b>110-client.json</b></p>
<pre class="code">
{
  "client" : {
    "VFS": {
      "Mountpoints": {
        "example": {
          "description": "Example"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>

<p><b>120-server.json</b></p>
<pre class="code">
{
  "server" : {
    "vfs": {
      "mounts": {
        "example": "/opt/example/directory"
      }
    }
  }
}
</pre>


<p>
  Then run:
</p>
<pre>grunt config</pre>
